======================================================================
PART 1: CARTAN DETERMINANT SEQUENCE AND SIMPLEX PACKING
======================================================================

  The Cartan matrix A_{n-1} encodes the type A root system.
  Its determinant is the index [weight lattice : root lattice] = n.

  n= 2: det(A_1) =    2, n! =        2, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/2, eigenvalue range [2.000, 2.000]
  n= 3: det(A_2) =    3, n! =        6, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/6, eigenvalue range [1.000, 3.000]
  n= 4: det(A_3) =    4, n! =       24, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/24, eigenvalue range [0.586, 3.414]
  n= 5: det(A_4) =    5, n! =      120, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/120, eigenvalue range [0.382, 3.618]
  n= 6: det(A_5) =    6, n! =      720, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/720, eigenvalue range [0.268, 3.732]
  n= 7: det(A_6) =    7, n! =     5040, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/5040, eigenvalue range [0.198, 3.802]
  n= 8: det(A_7) =    8, n! =    40320, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/40320, eigenvalue range [0.152, 3.848]
  n= 9: det(A_8) =    9, n! =   362880, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/362880, eigenvalue range [0.121, 3.879]
  n=10: det(A_9) =   10, n! =  3628800, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/3628800, eigenvalue range [0.098, 3.902]
  n=11: det(A_10) =   11, n! = 39916800, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/39916800, eigenvalue range [0.081, 3.919]
  n=12: det(A_11) =   12, n! = 479001600, vol(orthoscheme) = 1/479001600, eigenvalue range [0.068, 3.932]

  KEY: det(A₁) = 2, det(A₂) = 3 — these are the tournament keys!
  det(A_{n-1}) = n means n is fundamentally a 'Cartan index'.

  CHEBYSHEV PRODUCT IDENTITY:
  n = ∏_{k=1}^{n-1} (2 - 2cos(kπ/n))

  n=2: ∏ = 2.000000 (should be 2)
  n=3: ∏ = 3.000000 (should be 3)
  n=4: ∏ = 4.000000 (should be 4)
  n=5: ∏ = 5.000000 (should be 5)
  n=6: ∏ = 6.000000 (should be 6)
  n=7: ∏ = 7.000000 (should be 7)
  n=8: ∏ = 8.000000 (should be 8)
  n=9: ∏ = 9.000000 (should be 9)

  This connects to cyclotomic polynomials:
  Φ_n(2) = ∏_{gcd(k,n)=1} (2 - 2cos(2πk/n))

  Φ_n(2) values:
    Φ_ 1(2) = 1
    Φ_ 2(2) = 3
    Φ_ 3(2) = 7
    Φ_ 4(2) = 5
    Φ_ 5(2) = 31
    Φ_ 6(2) = 3
    Φ_ 7(2) = 127
    Φ_ 8(2) = 17
    Φ_ 9(2) = 73
    Φ_10(2) = 11
    Φ_11(2) = 2047
    Φ_12(2) = 13
    Φ_13(2) = 8191
    Φ_14(2) = 43
    Φ_15(2) = 151

